.DS_Store

# Dogfood state: running `sscsb init` on this repo generates the files below.
# They are regenerable (the walkthrough in docs/example-walkthrough.md shows the
# full set), so they are not committed — committing generated bootstrap output
# alongside the hand-authored templates that produce it would only confuse a
# reviewer about which is which. The tool's own CI is .github/workflows/ci.yml.
/.sscsb/
/.gitleaks.toml
/.trufflehog.yaml
/renovate.json5
/.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md
/.github/chainguard/
/.github/workflows/secrets-scan.yml
/.github/workflows/sbom.yml
/.github/workflows/vuln-scan.yml
/.github/workflows/scorecard.yml
/.github/workflows/release-sign.yml
/.github/workflows/release-slsa.yml
/.github/workflows/deploy-gate.yml
/.github/workflows/octo-sts-example.yml
/.github/workflows/sast-opengrep.yml
/.github/workflows/codeql.yml

# Agent worktrees from the coverage build-out.
/.claude/
